Class ElevatorFullException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • cscie55.hw3.exceptions.ElevatorFullException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ElevatorFullException
extends java.lang.Exception
    This class represents an exception to be thrown when the Elevator is full and one more passenger tries to be loaded onto.
    See Also:
